{"tid":346842,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[Asshole仔的抉擇] BU 英文系 vs CityU 英文系","createTime":"2017-08-04T09:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T06:21:51.000Z","uid":14216,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9eccf0867b3fc852313bbb9113444e021e7c41","tid":346842,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔先：Asshole仔走後門+讀BA乞食+唔好系我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我本身收到BU嘅English Language and Literature offer<br />\n已經課金咗一萬，準備下星期去reg day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我今朝收到City嘅English Studies offer，佢要我下星期二之前交錢覆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩科都係Senior Entry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知揀邊科好，學校嚟講我鍾意BU多啲，夠摺同啱我呢啲毒撚多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我啲朋友叫我揀City，因為排夠高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋有intern，讀business english簡單啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我之前睇連登又話BU文科好啲，又插City呢科係公廁嚟因為Nonjupas收70個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知點揀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想聽意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心急人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171f27c884e09d1efa31ab57fe47f6972435311a","tid":346842,"uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"City<br />\nHKU MBBS 收 2xx 個添，係咪更加公廁？"},{"pid":"9bf1c5bfcc73da7f8cc895636e20705aa15483f8","tid":346842,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>City<br />\nHKU MBBS 收 2xx 個添，係咪更加公廁？</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我收返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為都係聽同學講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無意得罪任何學校/科嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826a56bd6994e85ced81a889dc43700d89d55286","tid":346842,"uid":48012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"Shitty"},{"pid":"5424d7a8219db6cc92ee4cc489b0e257998d8534","tid":346842,"uid":60115,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>City<br />\nHKU MBBS 收 2xx 個添，係咪更加公廁？</blockquote><br />\n[<span style=\"color: red;\">City呢科係公廁嚟因為<del>Nonjupas</del>asshole收70個</span>]<br />\nmbbs係一隻asshole仔都唔會收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17300037f6b0f85220915f4dbae2a0b7c9770d3","tid":346842,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"Cityu"},{"pid":"6e4ac1c4932237a85a6f5216670a8f2f670fdaa8","tid":346842,"uid":14216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>City<br />\nHKU MBBS 收 2xx 個添，係咪更加公廁？</blockquote><br